Cylinder Services


Our core business at Millennium Technologies is our proprietary Nickel Silicon Carbide (NSC) cylinder plating process and cylinder services. This NSC process is so superior to factory plating that Millennium Technologies is often used by professional race teams all over the world to re-plate brand new OEM cylinders. We stand behind our plating with a LIMITED LIFETIME WARRANTY. Along with the proprietary plating process, Millennium Technologies is the world leader in cylinder repair, cylinder overbore services, 2-stroke cylinder porting services, power valve services, automotive services, big bore kits, and several specialized “custom” cylinder services. We also keep a huge inventory of repaired cylinders in stock for quick exchange. 


Related Services
Cylinder Plating
Modern engine designs use very light aluminum cylinders. The aluminum base metal is very soft and would wear out almost instantly without a very special protective barrier. The Millennium Technologies Nickel Silicon Carbide (NSC) cylinder plating process forms an extremely hard, extremely durable barrier with less friction, improved heat transfer, less weight, and ultimately more horsepower. We stand behind our plating with a LIFETIME WARRANTY. 
Click Here for More Info

Cylinder Repair
At Millennium Technologies, we perform miracles. If a cylinder can be saved, then we can save it and in turn save you money! Our flat-rate repair service is an all-inclusive cylinder emergency room. Crashed pistons, dropped valves, broken skirts, detonation, broken rings… we don’t care. Our evaluation service is free so before you throw that cylinder away, give us a chance to bring it back from the dead.
Click Here for More Info

Cylinder Overbore Services
There is no replacement for displacement! Millennium Technologies is the overbore specialist. With almost 20 years of overbore experience combined with our best in class Nickel Silicon Carbide (NSC) cylinder plating process, nobody has more experience making your motor bigger!
Click Here for More Info

Cylinder Exchange
Nobody likes to wait. We keep thousands of cylinders in stock, ready for exchange to get your powersports vehicle up and running, and better than new, as fast as possible. 
Click Here for More Info

M-Spec Big Bore Kits
Almost 20 years of increasing the displacement of internal combustion engines has made Millennium Technologies the leader in big bore kit technology. We offer complete, fully developed big bore kits for a huge variety of powersports applications including 2-stroke and 4-stroke off-road bikes, sport bikes, ATV/UTV, snowmobile, and watercraft.
Click Here for More Info

Revolution Performance Big Bore Kits
Famous Revolution Performance Big Bore Kits for your Harley-Davidson or Buell motorcycle. Monster kits require case boring service.
Click Here for More Info

Power Valve Service
Power valves are built into 2-Stroke cylinders around the exhaust port. They make the exhaust port bigger when you twist the throttle open giving you more power at higher rpm without sacrificing low rpm grunt. Power valves are complicated mechanisms prone to failure. We offer a service to clean, inspect, and adjust the powervalves. Click here to learn how Millennium Technologies can increase the power of your power valve.
Click Here for More Info

M-Spec Two-Stroke Performance Services
Millennium Technologies offers a complete line of high-performance 2-Stroke services including M-Spec big-bore kits, cylinder porting, head and base machining services along with our best in class Nickel Silicon Carbide (NSC) cylinder plating process. Learn how Millennium Technologies can make your 2-Stroke fly!
Click Here for More Info

Automotive Cylinder Services
Millennium Technologies offers full suite of automotive cylinder repair, plating, and overbore services. 
Click Here for More Info

Specialized Cylinder Services
Millennium Technologies is the world leader in cylinder services. If it can be done, we can do it. We offer a complete line of specialized cylinder services from installing heli-coils to complete custom designed billet cylinders.
Click Here for More Info

Cast Iron Services
Millennium Technologies specializes in Nickel Silicone Carbide (NSC) plating of aluminum cylinders, but we still offer a wide variety of services for cast iron cylinders.
Click Here for More Info

 




 
  


