Returns Policy




  Click icon above to download a printable PDF RGA form.


				If you can’t open PDF files, click this icon to get Adobe’s free Acrobat Reader.
We will take back anything we sell if we receive it within thirty days after you receive it. There is a 20% re-stocking fee charged against all returned parts. We cannot take back used or installed parts, even if only installed to test fitment. Parts must be resalable and in their original packaging. Call us at 1-888-779-6885 to arrange for any returned products. Please include a copy of your invoice with the return. We reserve the right not to accept any parts for return that we find to have been installed, used, or not in compliance with the above return criteria. Shipping and/or handling is also non-refundable. Thank you for your understanding.





 


 
 





  
 
 

