Footer 
About Private Flight Network, LLC
Private Flight Network, LLC is not a part 135 air carrier and only acts as an agent to provide info on the best carrier available for charter. Private Flight Network, LLC arranges flights on behalf of jet charter clients with FAR Part 135 air carriers that exercise full operational control of charter flights at all times. Flights will be operated by FAR Part 135 direct air carriers that have been certified to provide service for PFN clients and that meet all FAA safety standards and additional safety standards established by Private Flight Network.



